  <h3 id="v0100-breaking">Breaking Changes</h3>
  <p>
    <strong><code>sqlparse</code> is now a core dependency</strong> — it is installed automatically with <code>pip install araxys</code>. No code changes are required on your end. The library is used for SQL injection detection in the sanitization module, supplementing the existing 16 regex patterns with AST-based analysis.
  </p>

  <!-- Upgrading to v0.10 -->
