  <p>
    All v0.10.x features are <strong>opt-in</strong>. Your existing <code>AraxysConfig</code> continues to work unchanged. New modules (WebAuthn, Redis Sentinel/Cluster, Webhook DLQ, Session Idle Timeout) only activate when their config sections are populated. <strong>sqlparse</strong> is now always installed as a core dependency — no action needed.
